data.comment: The whistle has gone to start the match.
AIK's Mikael Lustig misses with an attempt on goal.
In the minute 2, Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
Throw-in Mjallby.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.

Throw-in for Mjallby at Friends Arena.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 7, AIK push forward at Friends Arena and Mikael Lustig gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Mjallby defence.
Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 10, It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
Important block from the Mjallby defence as Sebastian Larsson fires in a strike for AIK.
AIK have a dangerous throw-in.

Mjallby to take a throw-in in AIK territory.
Corner awarded to Mjallby.
In the minute 16, AIK have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
At Friends Arena, Eric Kahl for the home team has been yellow-carded. He will miss the next match due to a suspension!
In the minute 17, AIK's Nabil Bahoui gets in a shot on goal at Friends Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Corner awarded to AIK.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.

Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.

AIK drive upfield and Nabil Bahoui gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Mjallby defender.
In the minute 25, Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Adam Ladeback awards the home team a throw-in.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
In the minute 28, Sebastian Larsson for AIK gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Adam Ladeback awards Mjallby a goal kick.
AIK needs to be cautious. Mjallby have an attacking throw-in.
In the minute 31, AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
Can AIK get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Mjallby's half?
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 34, In Solna AIK attack through Nabil Bahoui. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Mjallby at Friends Arena.
AIK's Eric Kahl gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Mjallby defender.

Adam Ladeback signals a Mjallby throw-in in AIK's half.
Filip Rogic (AIK) gets in a powerful header but the ball is cleared away.
In the minute 38, In Solna Mjallby drive forward through Moses Ogbu. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 42, Throw-in for AIK in the half of Mjallby.
AIK's Nabil Bahoui gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Nabil Bahoui of AIK gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 44, Mjallby have a goal kick.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in AIK's half?

Marcus Lantz is making the team's first substitution at Friends Arena with Besard Sabovic replacing Jesper Gustavsson.

Adam Ladeback signals a throw-in for Mjallby, close to AIK's area.
AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.

Free kick in a good position for AIK!

Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to AIK.

Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of AIK.

Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.

Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.

Corner awarded to Mjallby.

2 minutes will be added to the 2nd half in Solna.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Corner awarded to AIK.
It's 1-0 as the referee blows for full-time.
Moses Ogbu (Mjallby) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Nabil Bahoui heads in to make it 1-0 at Friends Arena.
